videos.description: 1H (16:55) PITT Sheldon Jeter made Dunk. Assisted by Cameron Johnson.
videos.headline: Cameron Johnson finds Sheldon Jeter for baseline slam

videos.description: 1H (16:25) SYR Tyler Lydon made Dunk. Assisted by John Gillon.
videos.headline: Tyler Lydon throws down the dunk on the break

videos.description: Syracuse goes on an epic run against Pittsburgh, including Tyler Lydon's 3-pointer to make it a 25-2 stretch for the Orange. Syracuse would eventually cap the run at 30-2.
videos.headline: Lydon's 3-pointer part of a Syracuse 30-2 run

videos.headline: Pair of Sheldon Jeter free throws breaks 30-2 Cuse run
Andrew White closes out and makes the big-time block

videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillon lobs a pass for Tyler Roberson who throws down a two-handed alley-oop dunk with authority.
videos.headline: Gillon and Roberson connect on alley-oop jam
